name: Dessa Harness Belt
description:
A harness belt that snaps around the neck. Made with the finest genuine leather, the texture and thickness is perfectly divine.

This piece is named the "Dessa" harness, a nickname for goddess. The design is both feminine and masculine, featuring a strip of leather that wraps around the neck and moves downward in a linear form, like a men's tie.  The belt creatures a sleek waistline as it wraps around and buckles in the back.  Any woman can conquer all in this powerful piece. 

Oxidized black steel ring detail at neck. Black buckle detail on front and back. Leather measures 3/4" wide. Ring is 1" in diameter. Belt buckle is 1" wide.

Fully adjustable at waist and length. Order your waist size in inches. Make sure to take measurement at the smallest part of your waist. Belt is adjustable up to 4 inches. Adjustable two snaps at the neck.

***Available for limited time only during Holiday Sales.  Will be release again in January 2014.

name: Blair Shoulder Chain
description:
The Blair Shoulder Chain.

Oozing with dark, witchy, and powerful vibes.

Black plated, lightweight aluminum chain is woven from shoulder to shoulder to create the illusion of a web. With a 3/4" strip of the finest leather stretching the length of the shoulders, and down the arm, this body chain becomes a full shoulder accessory, almost like sensual armor.

Two adjustable snaps sit at the base of the neck for sizing. Each arm cuff also has two adjustable snaps. The model is 5'4", wearing size S/M. 

If you're unsure about what size to order, remember that this piece is fully adjustable, with industrial grade snaps that will last a lifetime. 

This piece can also be custom made to fit your exact measurements. If you'd like a custom piece, please provide us with:

1. Circumference of your arm, right above the elbow. You can use a piece of string and stretch it along a ruler.
2. Length from right above the elbow (where the cuff will sit) to the top of your shoulder.
3. Circumference of your neck, at the base where it meets the shoulders
4. Length from the base of your neck to the end of your shoulder.

Each shoulder chain comes in a signature JAKIMAC burlap bag for safe keeping.

***Available for limited time only during Holiday Sales.  Will be release again in January 2014.
